{"type":null,"faqId":19646,"title":"荣耀6plus手机异常发热、发烫的判定，待机发热、无操作发热以及突然明显发热？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您好，1.正常发热的解释：手机在使用时发热程度有差异，正常信号下通话，发送短信，手机发热较少；拍照摄像、玩画面细致的游戏、上网浏览与下载图片文字，耗电和发热程度都会增加，这些都是正常的现象。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.异常发热的判定：如果您的手机在某个时间（手机中部和电源键附近的边框）发热突然增大，或在您仅简单操作甚至没有操作时发热非常明显，说明您的手机有应用程序在额外的耗电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.异常发热的处理：1、建议您进入“设置-&gt;省电管理-&gt;后台耗电应用”，查看后台耗电应用，并清理高耗电的应用，第三方卫士类软件持续占用手机CPU资源，容易导致发热和耗电快。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若以上方法未生效，请重新启动手机，观察现象是否消失。若还是无法解决，请您备份手机的数据，恢复出厂设置看此现象是否消失。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":15,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2866","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1423274189000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":1185,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀6plus,发热","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}